  m_sTitle "Mission notes"
  m_sTextData "<h2>End Conditions</h2>"\
  "<b>Iraq:</b>"\
  "Victory - Hold out for long enough to repel the Insurgent attack."\
  ""\
  "<b>Insuregents:</b>"\
  "Victory - OCCUPY the Iraqi checkpoint and ELIMINATE all garrisoning forces."\
  ""\
  "<h2>Restrictions</h2>"\
  "• Iraqi team is <b>forbidden</b> from digging trenches within the perimeter of the checkpoint."\
  "fortifying is allowed beyond the hesco walls. "\
  "ALL access routes must remain clear of player dug trenches, although vehicles can be used to block routes."\
  "• Iraqi team is <b>forbidden</b> from using their mortar untill setup timer end (2min)"\
  "• Iraqi mortar team is <b>forbidden</b> from firing upon INDFOR spawn or within a 200m radius."\
  ""\
  "<h2>Notes</h2>"\
  "• Setup timer: 2mins"
