 }
 SUM {
  coords 328.325 24.509 5704.552
  m_sTitle "Summary"
  m_sTextData "A major insurgent force is preparing to assault an Iraqi Army checkpoint north of Al-Hadra. The position controls a key stretch of highway that insurgent forces need secured in order to move men and equipment through the region freely."\
  "Outnumbered Iraqi defenders are expected to face a heavy attack as both sides fight for control of the route."\
  ""\
  "<b>Reference mission notes for restrictions</b>"
